##  Outcome
 -  **LANDED `08df5879`** (2026-06-16): guard the slot-overwrite unprotect in
    `JABCioMakeFileObject`, skip `close()` for fds 0/1/2 in `JABCioCloseFile`,
    dedup the stdio unprotect (null `JS_FILES[0..2]` before the close-loop), and
    `free(JS_FILES)` on uninstall; C++ harness now drives io install/uninstall
    and asserts std fds survive + table freed (red-before/green-after, ASAN/LSan
    clean). (a) fd-reuse GC-root balance is logic-verified; (b)+(c) test-verified.

